                                         "text":  "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgUniverseTimeBigBang\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgUniverseTimeBigBang', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figura 1</b>: El universo a través del espacio-tiempo (<htcite0>).</p>",
                                         "source":  [
